      value: Scene8_Chapter1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _StoryText
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _DialoguePanel
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _FadeTransition
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 2005903683}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _BlackScreenText
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _BlackScreenIndex
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _BlackScreenPanel
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentLines.Array.size
      value: 20
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: "You must be confused with what\u2019s going on but allow me to explain."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I am your journal and I am speaking to you right now.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: "This isn\u2019t possible, nanaginip siguro ako."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: "You\u2019re not dreaming this is all real, You are currently inside
        the Raymundo house back in the 1930s where the house was still at its prime
        along with the third generation of Raymundos that lived in the house."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: But why am I here?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: "To fulfill your wish of course! Isn\u2019t this what you wanted, a
        chance to save the house of YOUR distant family?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: "I do remember wishing for a way to save the house, but I didn\u2019t
        expect the solution would be something as insane as this\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: How do I even save the house, why am I a kid,  and how do I even go
        back to my own time?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: By doing what you should have done in the Raymundo house.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: Taking care of the home and writing down every significant detail you
        find, get curious!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentSpeakers.Array.size
      value: 20
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: To get you started tap on the small journal icon at the top of the screen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: "In this page you\u2019ll find a list of certain tasks you need to do
        to help you progress through the day."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[12]'
      value: "Here\u2019s your first task of the day."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[13]'
      value: Make sure to complete every single one of the tasks so that you can
        learn more about the Raymundo house and the family.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[14]'
      value: And maybe you can even find a secret or two.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[15]'
      value: Next, click on the bookmark with the [icon] on the tab.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[16]'
      value: in this page you can keep track of every artifact you find and log.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[17]'
      value: As you can see there are already three artifacts you managed to log
        from the present day.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[18]'
      value: Certain conditions and information of certain artifacts can be added
